%^BOLD%^-=%^BLACK%^Darkness Domain%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

By channelling the powers of darkness, the caster can 
create a range of spells that protect him, cause damage 
to his foes, and finally allow him to spy upon those who 
are far away.

The darkness domain contains the following spells:
Armor of Darkness (3rd), Darkbolt (5th), and Listening Shadow (8th)

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Lord Shadow, The Faceless One

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
     